title: LF Silver/Gold Duo Partner

embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body: finding it hardd to climb outta silver.. currently silver 4.. Check my op.gg out and chuck us an add if you're interested to duo ranked with me

replies.body:
I'm happy to... as long as you don't mind playing with an Annie OTP. S5, play Annie mid/top/support (in that order)

I'm not toxic at all, and pretty chill, as long as you are as well.

Drawback is I don't spam league, only a few games a day in the hols, and on the weekend only during term. 

You interested?
Yea sure man, i only play on weekends too
